author: sussman
msg: Lots more book stuff.
* appb.xml:  new appendix documenting cvs2svn.py, to some small degree.
* rcsparse.py:  added to cvs2svn/ dir, so people can stop asking where
to get it!  please!
* appa.xml (Binary files):  add internal binary-diff explanation.
* ch05.xml:  expand our explanation of how to run svnserve, and how to
set up ssh tunneling.  Also, add a honest comparison of
reasons to run either mod_dav_svn or svnserve.
* ch06.xml (Servers):  uncomment the 'svn-tunnel-agent' documentation.
* ch07.xml (RA-SVN):  add one more paragraph.
